{
  "title": "Bitter Juicy Goan Chickpea Curry",
  "description": "A pescatarian-friendly Goan curry featuring chickpeas, with a balance of bitter and juicy flavors, perfect for a festive meal. This dish is made with a can of chickpeas and a blend of Indian spices.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
  "diet": [
